      "content": "I'd be happy to help you create a professional summary. Here's a concise and accurate version:\n\n\"The patient presents with a two-day history of severe headaches, dizziness upon standing, palpitations, and unilateral redness and itching around the eyes. These symptoms may indicate a possible vascular or allergic etiology, warranting further evaluation.\"\n\nThis summary maintains a relevant 'clinical depth' without relying on overly complex language or artificially inflated medical terminology, ensuring the doctor can effectively understand the patient's condition.",
